reviewText: I love this series and the quality of the DVD are pretty good.

When i finally found this title on DVD, it took me a few weeks to save up the money for it. However, when i did finally order it, it arrived swiftly and in beautiful condition. I only wish that the DVDs inside were in something more than just the little book-pouch thing, however, i do tend to get pissed off at the hard plastic "pages" that are found inside of most multi-disk items so i guess that beggars can't be choosers.
Just brilliant. Cannot express how much I love this drama and the box set arrived in perfect condition. Very happy with my purchase. Great price too.
